{"tid":2216364,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"個同事褲袋成日袋到一舊二舊 今日無聊行埋去問佢咩事","createTime":"2020-09-24T15:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T08:47:08.000Z","uid":51346,"like":13,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"14f83be2751af875771a48f726492d2426169b2c","tid":2216364,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T15:06:31.000Z","msg":"我＝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   個同事＝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老細＝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 靚女同事＝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我： 喂 xx （xx係佢個名） 你褲袋成日袋到一舊二舊腫起咗咁 其實袋住啲咩 你幫人運貨呀？<br />\n<br />\n佢：無呀 左邊袋手機 耳機 紙巾 右邊袋銀包 鎖匙 員工卡咋嘛<br />\n<br />\n我：哇 好方便喎 想要咩就拎到 但你唔覺腫起咗咁好肉酸咩 咁樣溝唔到女架（搭佢膊頭）<br />\n<br />\n佢：覺呀 但為咗保護後代無法啦<br />\n<br />\n我：保護後代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢：我返工放工條路好多流浪狗 袋到腫起成個春袋咁 啲狗咪得3份1機會咬中我春袋囉<br />\n<br />\n我：＋－&times;&divide;＝％"},{"pid":"d915ec1e4ea0c5c21dd40082aaf4e4731a5d2bbf","tid":2216364,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T15:07:26.000Z","msg":"唔好笑 but 1"},{"pid":"87d5074e2740cf453eb7f00b99654967c9293974","tid":2216364,"uid":374184,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T15:07:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"90c5e0d7476dbe35c9c6b5fb0adc99f50cba911b","tid":2216364,"uid":207530,"like":